---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
export const prerender = true;
---

<Layout title="About Us">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About Agnostic News</h1>
        <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
            <p>Welcome to Agnostic News, your number one source for unbiased news. We're dedicated to giving you the very best of reporting, with a focus on objectivity, clarity, and depth.</p>
            <p>Founded in 2025, Agnostic News has come a long way from its beginnings. When we first started out, our passion for truth in journalism drove us to create a platform where readers could find news without the noise. We now serve readers all over the world, and are thrilled that we're able to turn our passion into our own website.</p>
            <p>We hope you enjoy our articles as much as we enjoy offering them to you. If you have any questions or comments, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
